/backup-vault-locally.content:
Backs up vault here: `X:\obsidian-backups` as zip every 2 hours.

Script also in [GitHub Gist](https://gist.github.com/janeilagan/612d4ca39d20002e1bb7d29acd885031) 

````powershell
#Auto task to zip and backup obsidian vault
$vaultPath = "C:\Users\janea\OneDrive\capsule"
$backupname = "X:\obsidian-backups\capsule-$(get-date -f yyyy-MMM-dd-hhmmsstt)-$env:computername-BAK.zip"

try {

Compress-Archive -Path $vaultPath -DestinationPath $backupname -CompressionLevel NoCompression
Write-Host "Successful"

}catch {

Write-Error -Message "Close Obsidian!"

}

````
